sentences: Gerry Niewood (April 6, 1943 – February 12, 2009), born Gerard Joseph Nevidosky, was an American jazz saxophonist and flautist who worked often with Chuck Mangione.
He worked with Mangione from 1968 to 1976 and shortly after led a band with Dave Samuels.
In the 1990s, he returned to playing with Mangione.
He and band member Coleman Mellett died in the crash of Colgan Air Flight 3407 on February 12, 2009.
